  "body": "## Feature request\r\n\r\nWhen testing smart contracts in Solidity, there is magical `truffle/DeployedAddresses.sol` to obtain the address at which the contract has been deployed. But there is no really way to obtain the address which created the contract, or send transactions from that address. So one cannot verify for example if the contract has correctly stored who is the owner of the contract.\r\n\r\n",
